title: Follow 2015 District 11 girls tennis singles tournaments (BRACKETS)
text:
Wilson's Tyra Ott is into the District 11 Class AA quarterfinals. (lehighvalleylive.com file photo) By Josh Folck | For lehighvalleylive.com on October 07, 2015 8:18 PM, updated October 07, 2015 8:52 PM View/Post Comments 
The District 11 Class AA and AAA girls tennis singles tournaments got started on Wednesday at Parkland High School. 
The seeded players in each bracket advanced to the quarterfinals except for unseeded Skyler Hammond of Moravian Academy making the final eight in Class AA. 
The quarterfinals and semifinals for both classes will be held on Thursday at Parkland High School. 
The championship matches for both classes are set for Monday at Lehigh University.
